value.title: Rigetti and ADIA Lab Sign Collaboration Agreement to Develop Quantum Machine Learning Solution for Probability Distribution Classification
value.excerpt: Rigetti Computing, Inc. (Nasdaq: RGTI) (“Rigetti” or the “Company”), a pioneer in full-stack quantum-classical computing, today announced that it has signed a collaboration agreement with ADIA Lab, an independent Abu-Dhabi-based institute dedicated to basic and applied research in data and computational sciences.
